==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inchon
<hw>Inchon</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The name of a town in Korea and
of a battle in the Korean War (1950), in which United Nations forces
made an amphibious landing at Inchon, a harbor on the west coast of
Korea.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

